{
  "stem": "6277.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So from this day on, my birthday converted in a mourning day.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Till now, this-- I never celebrate the day.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I'm fasting, the day, remembering them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So it's more than 50 years.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The small ghetto-- as we came to the small ghetto, it was the 8th.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When it was 8th of December, took place a second-- action number two.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The next day, we called it later, was the 'Bloody Tuesday.' The Bloody Tuesday, they were chasing-- they were searching all the houses who lived-- who lived there, and taking everyone who was in the ghetto who wasn't working in the day.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was my-- my fate or luck.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I-- I-- I went to work.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And when we came back, there were again-- I don't know how many people were taken again, or-- some of them to the cemetery, the Jewish cemetery, they called.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We had close to the ghetto, actually.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "In the ghetto, we had the-- an old Jewish cemetery.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They were taken to the old Jewish cemetery and killed.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Some of them were taken to the Rumbula Forest again and killed there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Who were work--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Some of them who lived in the big ghetto.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they didn't-- some of them hided.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Some of them were by accident, they were taken to the action.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they chased every house.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then they came to the small ghetto, and they took the people who were home-- it was at daytime-- who weren't at work.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they took-- children were different stories, you know?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They took children.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They took adults.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They took everyone who was at home at that-- in that day.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So not everyone in the small ghetto was a working man or a boy.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There were children there?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, it was-- officially, it was working people.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
